{"type": "article", "id": 22749, "title": "带6个镂空小块的滑板", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-24T07:30:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150700Vwt2GMqYgQ3uOZlD.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是美国设计师 Joey Ruiter 带来的滑板，使用略带方形的木板制作。特别在于中间和四个角落的镂空，让它显得干净利落。4 个角落对应了滚轮的位置，倾斜时恰好卡在空出来的地方，而中间的镂空是用方便脚尖插入帮助暂停的。售价 295 美元，<a href=\"http://www.blessthisstuff.com/stuff/vehicles/misc/lo-ruiter-longboard/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150658hObzXxkCWoREeVD7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.67802385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150659ctvr7J5yDwkEMxgb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67802385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150659ZAx3mo2N6h7dSiJr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40374787\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150659dH0bvfzYtpAe4aV7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40374787\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}